metadata.name: ShinwaArtNFT_HBRTTM000001_otbo_wcp_banksy_pulp_fiction_99/500
metadata.description: Shinwa Art NFT leaves a trace in the ERC721 Ethereum blockchain platform managed by Shinwa Art Blockchain based on Zendoo, a sidechain of Horizen. HBRTTM (“Honey Badger Rockets To The Moon”) project leaves a graffiti on the back of a reproduction piece of Banksy printed by The West Country Prince and creates a NFT to give us a trace where the NFT was sold.
